# API: default is Supabase Edge (same project as login). No variable needed for production.
#
# Optional override — only ABSOLUTE URLs are used:
#   VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://your-custom-host.com/api
# (If it ends with /api, /make-server-d5ac9b81 is appended automatically.)
#
# Do NOT set VITE_API_BASE_URL=/api on Vercel — it is ignored and caused 404s.
#
# For Edge auth + data to work, deploy the function in this repo to Supabase and set:
#   SUPABASE_JWT_SECRET (Edge Function secret)
